{"title_page": "Rupa, Croatia", "text_new": "'''Rupa''' ({{lang-it|Ruppa}}) is a village in northwest [[Croatia]] near its border with [[Slovenia]]. It is located in [[Matulji]] ({{lang-it|Mattuglie}}) municipality in [[Primorje-Gorski Kotar County]], 17 km from the town of Matulji. It has a population of 310 (census 2001).<ref>{{Cite web | url=http://www.dzs.hr/hrv/censuses/census2001/Popis/H01_01_03/h01_01_03_zup08-2615.html |title = SAS Output}}</ref>\n\nRupa is a major border crossing between the two countries where Croatia's Autocesta [[A7 (Croatia)|A7]] motorway connects with Slovenia's [[Highways in Slovenia|Highway 7]]. The Slovenian town opposite Rupa is [[Jel\u0161ane]] in [[Ilirska Bistrica]] municipality. With Slovenia joining the [[Schengen area]] on December 21, 2007, Rupa-Jel\u0161ane became a Schengen external border crossing.\n\nRupa je kraljevstvo z 7000 stanovniki i 3 velika mosta ispod kih protje\u010de rijeka CESTA.\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n{{coord|45.478|N|14.286|E|source:hrwiki_region:HR|format=dms|display=title}}\n\n[[Category:Croatia\u2013Slovenia border crossings]]\n[[Category:Populated places in Primorje-Gorski Kotar County]]\n", "text_old": "'''Rupa''' ({{lang-it|Ruppa}}) is a village in northwest [[Croatia]] near its border with [[Slovenia]]. It is located in [[Matulji]] ({{lang-it|Mattuglie}}) municipality in [[Primorje-Gorski Kotar County]], 17 km from the town of Matulji. It has a population of 310 (census 2001).<ref>{{Cite web | url=http://www.dzs.hr/hrv/censuses/census2001/Popis/H01_01_03/h01_01_03_zup08-2615.html |title = SAS Output}}</ref>\n\nRupa is a major border crossing between the two countries where Croatia's Autocesta [[A7 (Croatia)|A7]] motorway connects with Slovenia's [[Highways in Slovenia|Highway 7]]. The Slovenian town opposite Rupa is [[Jel\u0161ane]] in [[Ilirska Bistrica]] municipality. With Slovenia joining the [[Schengen area]] on December 21, 2007, Rupa-Jel\u0161ane became a Schengen external border crossing.\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n{{coord|45.478|N|14.286|E|source:hrwiki_region:HR|format=dms|display=title}}\n\n[[Category:Croatia\u2013Slovenia border crossings]]\n[[Category:Populated places in Primorje-Gorski Kotar County]]\n", "name_user": "31.45.226.72", "label": "unsafe", "comment": "(Added content)", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Rupa,_Croatia"}
