ries)|Charlotte]]'' || Leader (Ep. 13)\n|-\n| 2018 || ''[[Re:Zero \u2212 Starting Life in Another World]]'' || Kan\n|-\n| 2018 || ''[[JoJo's Bizarre Adventure: Stardust Crusaders]]'' || Nukesaku\n|-\n| 2018 || ''[[Saint Seiya: The Lost Canvas]]'' || Pegasus Tenma\n|-\n| 2018 || ''[[March Comes in Like a Lion]]'' || Eisaku Noguchi\n|-\n| 2019 || ''[[KonoSuba|KonoSuba: God's Blessing on this Wonderful World!]]'' || Kazuma Sat\u014d\n|-\n| 2019 || ''[[Isekai Quartet]]'' || Kazuma Sat\u014d\n|}\n\n===Western Animation===\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n! Years !! Titles !! Roles !! Notes\n|-\n| 2018 || ''[[We Bare Bears]]'' || Chuckles, Knives ||\n|-\n| 2018 || ''[[Spirit Riding Free]]'' || Calvin ||\n|-\n| 2018 || ''[[Trolls: The Beat Goes On!]]'' || Archer Pastry ||\n|}\n\n===Live action TV Series===\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n! Years !! Titles !! Roles !! Notes\n|-\n| 2017 || ''[[Scorpion (TV series)|Scorpion]]'' || Nightingale || Episode: \"Faire Is Foul\"\n|-\n| 2018 || ''[[Lucifer (TV series)|Lucifer]]'' || Simon || Episode: \"A Devil of My Word\"\n|-\n| 2018 || ''[[Henry Danger]]'' || Mark || Episode: \"Thumb War\"\n|-\n| 2019 || ''[[Into the Dark (TV series)|Into the Dark]]'' || Eddie || Episode: \"Down\"\n|-\n| 2019 || ''[[Superstore (TV series)|Superstore]]'' || Dad Customer || Episode: \"Cloud 9 Academy\"\n|}\n\n===Video Games===\n\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n! Years !! Titles !! Roles !! Notes\n|-\n| 2020 || ''[[Final Fantasy VII Remake]]'' || Reno || <ref>[https://square-enix-games.com/en_US/news/final-fantasy-vii-remake-voice-actors Meet the English voice cast for FINAL FANTASY VII REMAKE]</ref>\n|-\n|}\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n* {{IMDb name|2099549}}\n* {{ann|people|151189}}\n\n{{authority control}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Pantoja, Arnie}}\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:American male film actors]]\n[[Category:American male television actors]]\n[[Category:American male voice actors]]\n[[Category:Male actors from Kansas City, 