rose issue #1 (2018)\n\n== References ==\n<references />\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Gross, Daerick Sr.}}\n[[Category:Fantasy artists]]\n[[Category:American illustrators]]\n[[Category:American speculative fiction artists]]\n[[Category:People from Simi Valley, California]]\n[[Category:1947 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n", "name_user": "Alistair1978", "label": "safe", "comment": "typo (viaWP:JWB)", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/D%C3%A6rick_Gr%C3%B6ss_Sr."}
